.TH wxWindowCreateEvent 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxWindowCreateEvent \- This event is sent just after the actual window associated with a \fIwxWindow\fR object has been created.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Since it is derived from \fIwxCommandEvent\fR, the event propagates up the window hierarchy.

